title: Complete Genome Sequencing of a Novel Strain of Sapelovirus A Circulating in Vietnam
body: The genome sequence of the XTND/2018 strain has been deposited in DDBJ/ENA/GenBank (accession number LC493088). The raw sequence reads were deposited in the DDBJ Sequence Read Archive (DRA) under the BioProject and DRA accession numbers PRJDB8629 and DRA008757, respectively.
